24 February 2014Members of the media are invited to a post State of Nation Address Public Service and Administration Cluster media briefing.Public Service and Administration Minister Lindiwe Sisulu will lead the media briefing. Minister Sisulu will be joined by Home Affairs Minister Naledi Pandor; Sport and Recreation Minister Fikile Mbalula and Arts and Culture Minister Paul Mashatile.Details are as follows:Date: Tuesday, 25 February 2014 Time: 10h00 Venue: Media Centre, Cape Town, ParliamentNB: There will be a video-link to GCIS media briefing room, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard, Corner Festival Street, Hatfield, Pretoria RSVP: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) Cell: 072 822 5869 E-mail: ireen@gcis.gov.za Shadi Baloyi (Cape Town) Cell: 076 9467 136 E-mail: shadib@gcis.gov.za Enquiries: Ndivhuwo Mabaya Contact: 083 645 7838Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)